# ~/.offload-config — offload tool configuration
# Copy this to ~/.offload-config and edit for your setup.
# Lines starting with # are comments. Blank lines ignored.
# The script re-reads this file on every invocation — no restart needed.

# ─── Mount points ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# macOS:
EXT_MOUNT=/Volumes/MyDrive
EXT_HOME=/Volumes/MyDrive/home

# Linux example:
# EXT_MOUNT=/mnt/external
# EXT_HOME=/mnt/external/home

# ─── Symlinks ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Format: SYMLINK|<source-relative-to-$HOME>|<absolute-target>|<description>
# Add one line per directory you want to live on the external disk.
# Run: offload scan   — to see candidates with their sizes.

# Developer toolchains (high value — these are large and rarely change)
SYMLINK|.cargo|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.cargo|Rust toolchain
SYMLINK|.rustup|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.rustup|Rust versions
SYMLINK|.pyenv|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.pyenv|Python versions (pyenv)
SYMLINK|go|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/go|Go workspace

# Package caches
SYMLINK|.npm|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.npm|npm cache
SYMLINK|.yarn|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.yarn|yarn cache
SYMLINK|.bun|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.bun|bun runtime + cache
SYMLINK|.gradle|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.gradle|Gradle cache
SYMLINK|.pub-cache|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.pub-cache|Dart/Flutter pub cache
SYMLINK|.gem|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.gem|Ruby gems (system)

# AI / model data (can be very large)
# SYMLINK|.ollama|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/.ollama|Ollama models

# Git / project directories (optional — only if they're large)
# SYMLINK|GitHub|/Volumes/MyDrive/home/GitHub|All git repos

# ─── Services ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Format: SERVICE|<name>|<start-command>|<stop-command>|<check-command>
# Check command: exit 0 = running, non-zero = stopped.
# Add services whose data lives on the external disk.

# SERVICE|podman|podman machine start|podman machine stop|podman machine list --format '{{.Running}}' | grep -q true
# SERVICE|ollama|ollama serve > /tmp/ollama.log 2>&1 &|pkill -x ollama|pgrep -x ollama

# ─── Never-symlink list ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Format: NEVER|<name>|<reason>
# These will be skipped by `offload scan` and rejected by `offload add`.

NEVER|.ssh|Permissions sensitive — must stay local
NEVER|.config|Shell startup dependency — must stay local
NEVER|Library|macOS-managed — do not move
NEVER|Documents|iCloud sync
NEVER|Desktop|User intent
NEVER|Downloads|User intent
NEVER|Applications|System-managed
NEVER|Movies|User data
NEVER|Music|User data
NEVER|Pictures|iCloud Photos
NEVER|.Trash|System
NEVER|.zshrc|Shell config — must stay local
NEVER|.zsh_history|Shell history — must stay local
NEVER|.gitconfig|Small + startup dependency
